# Bug Retesting and Verification

## Description

This educational project was completed during the QA Engineer program at Yandex Practicum.

## Objective

The objective of this project was to retest previously reported defects, verify bug fixes, and update bug statuses.

## What I did

- Performed bug retesting.
- Verified implemented bug fixes.
- Updated bug statuses.
- Documented testing results.

